abstract: Madison, Wis, Police Officer Matt Kenny is cleared of charges in March shooting death of unarmed biracial man Tony Robinson; move clears way for Kenny to return to force.
lead_paragraph: A white Madison police officer was exonerated Wednesday by an internal investigation into his fatal shooting of an unarmed 19-year-old biracial man.

headline.main: Wisconsin: Internal Inquiry Clears Officer in Unarmed Man’s Killing
